{"tid":361354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過係街冇啦啦有人好心幫你？","createTime":"2017-08-16T05:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T06:57:09.000Z","uid":135491,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d896e9c6438620d08620136f945c7fe9d2e3616","tid":361354,"uid":135491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"好幾年前試過返屋企途中冇啦啦落狗屎<br />\n係橋底避左陣都冇停<br />\n個陣心諗 唉 屌豁出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遮都唔遮慢慢行返去<br />\n行多兩步 冇啦啦feel 到後面有人行埋黎遮我<br />\n我呆一呆都未反應得切  佢就講<br />\n&quot;咩咁大意唔記得帶遮呀&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n原來係靚女黎 未夠30歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我完全冇印象識佢或者見過佢<br />\n我個陣仲傻傻下 淨係答佢係呀 一齊行到樓下講聲多謝就走左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後都冇見過佢<br />\n但到而加都覺得香港有咁好既人真係好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdd9c47289742ab55284281fc3a9192af303f7f","tid":361354,"uid":135491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"邊個偷偷留負評就走#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ff2543da7b6375dc53d3328e147c3c63dce7a3","tid":361354,"uid":130145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"我幾年前都試過一樣既野 係學生妹黎 同我住同一座 但無講過野<br />\n<br />\n如果遮你個位係肥婆你會覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b06b0a0ce94cf10031a12db49fb5400e5254b4","tid":361354,"uid":60510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幾年前都試過一樣既野 係學生妹黎 同我住同一座 但無講過野<br />\n<br />\n如果遮你個位係肥婆你會覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遮到你遮唔到我呀，洗撚你遮咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"d2b0675836156491b80d9e4059b1c79ce