s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5156fa6a892e5c3820fcebdd1387adb292e016","tid":361354,"uid":87711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"有啊 之前等小巴返屋企 又係落狗屎 附近又冇瓦遮頭 焗住要淋住雨等 淋左陣就有位好心既哥哥過黎遮我 好多謝佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e699939b10d806e45905f7e17d39003635a25a","tid":361354,"uid":30171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T06:14:21.000Z","msg":"自己好心幫人就有。<br />\n<br />\n講起落雨我都試過喺路上好心遮埋人，見條友俾雨淋住噤等轉燈過馬路我就上前行埋去遮埋佢：「天文台話今日會落雨做咩唔帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，佢就即刻好好笑容話唔該晒，之後就同佢吹下水廢事唔出聲會尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(不過條友TB黎）</span>"},{"pid":"7f106b6fcb78099db819a99cf2a0d5ee636c02c8","tid":361354,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我幾年前都試過一樣既野 係學生妹黎 同我住同一座 但無講過野<br />\n<br />\n如果遮你個位係肥婆你會覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遮到你遮唔到我呀，洗撚你遮咩屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}